            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "地產｜新世界(00017)瑧玥原價加推最後34伙 折實408萬起",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"地產｜新世界(00017)瑧玥原價加推最後34伙 折實408萬起\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜新世界(00017)瑧玥原價加推最後34伙 折實408萬起</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新世界發展(00017)旗下佐敦官涌街瑧玥，原價加推2號價單，涉及餘下的34伙，折實售價408.6萬至683.3萬元，折實呎價19183至25785元，折實平均呎價23418元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新世界發展營業及市務部總監何家欣表示，是次加推單位大部分位於中高層，部分單位更可享中環及西九商業地標景觀。而是次加推10伙開放式戶維持「一口價」折實408.6萬元，屬近11年區內最平入場價，最快下周開售。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加推單位包括10伙開放式戶及24伙1房戶，實用面積171至266方呎。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑧玥提供64伙，實用面積171至266方呎，包括62伙標準單位及2伙連平台特色戶，全屬開放式及1房單位。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-00017-%E7%91%A7%E7%8E%A5%E5%8E%9F%E5%83%B9%E5%8A%A0%E6%8E%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C34%E4%BC%99-%E6%8A%98%E5%AF%A6408%E8%90%AC%E8%B5%B7-073912252.html",
